CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 20, 1946, pg. 17, reads: "Model - Miss Alma Rector, popular debutante, will be one of the models in annual fashion revue at Peabody High School, Tuesday, April 30, under sponsorship of St. James AME Church."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Alma Rector Collins wearing coat with three buttons, hat, and pearl choker, walking on path in park
